msgstr "Controlla come Jetonomy adotta i token di design del tuo tema attivo."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:749
msgid "Inherit from Theme"
msgstr "Eredita dal tema"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:754
msgid "Inherit theme fonts"
msgstr "Eredita i caratteri del tema"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:759
msgid "Inherit theme colors"
msgstr "Eredita i colori del tema"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:770
msgid "Logo"
msgstr "Logo"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:771
msgid ""
"Your community logo. Shown in the mobile app (login + header) and anywhere "
"a brand mark is needed. Square or wide PNG/SVG; leave empty to show the "
"Community Title as text."
msgstr ""
"Il logo della tua comunità. Mostrato nell'app mobile (accesso + "
"intestazione) e ovunque sia necessario un marchio. PNG/SVG quadrato o "
"largo; lascia vuoto per mostrare il Titolo della comunità come testo."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:775
msgid "Logo URL"
msgstr "URL del logo"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:778
msgid ""
"Paste an image URL (e.g. from Media Library). Recommended: at least 512px "
"on the longest side, transparent PNG."
msgstr ""
"Incolla un URL immagine (ad es. dalla Libreria media). Consigliato: almeno "
"512px sul lato più lungo, PNG trasparente."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:787
msgid "Color Palette"
msgstr "Tavolozza di colori"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:788
msgid ""
"Set the community colors directly — useful when your theme has no color "
"tokens for Jetonomy to inherit. Applied when \"Inherit theme colors\" is "
"off. Leave a field empty to keep the default; secondary shades (hover, "
"muted text) derive automatically."
msgstr ""
"Imposta i colori della comunità direttamente — utile quando il tuo tema non "
"ha token di colore per Jetonomy da ereditare. Applicato quando \"Eredita i "
"colori del tema\" è disattivato. Lascia un campo vuoto per mantenere il "
"valore predefinito; le tonalità secondarie (al passaggio del mouse, testo "
"attenuato) derivano automaticamente."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:792
msgid "Accent"
msgstr "Accento"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:795
msgid "Buttons, links, active states, and notification emails."
msgstr "Pulsanti, link, stati attivi ed email di notifica."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:799
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Testo"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:802
msgid "Body copy and headings. Secondary and muted text derive from it."
msgstr "Testo principale e titoli. Il testo secondario e attenuato ne derivano."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:806
msgid "Background"
msgstr "Sfondo"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:809
msgid "Cards and content surfaces."
msgstr "Schede e superfici di contenuto."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:813
msgid "Subtle Background"
msgstr "Sfondo Sottile"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:816
msgid "Secondary surfaces — table headers, code, quiet panels."
msgstr "Superfici secondarie — intestazioni di tabella, codice, pannelli tranquilli."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:820
msgid "Border"
msgstr "Bordo"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:823
msgid "Card outlines, dividers, and input borders."
msgstr "Contorni schede, divisori e bordi di input."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:838
msgid "Layout"
msgstr "Layout"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:839
msgid ""
"Control how community pages fit inside your active theme. \"Theme Default\" "
"leaves your theme in charge."
msgstr ""
"Controlla come le pagine della community si adattano al tuo tema attivo. "
"\"Tema Predefinito\" lascia il controllo al tuo tema."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:843
msgid "Container Width"
msgstr "Larghezza Contenitore"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:848 includes/admin/views/settings.php:872
#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:889
msgid "Theme Default"
msgstr "Tema Predefinito"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:853
msgid "Full Width"
msgstr "Larghezza Intera"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:858
