msgstr "Barra Laterale Tema"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:877
msgid "Hide on community pages"
msgstr "Nascondi nelle pagine della community"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:880
msgid ""
"Hides your theme's sidebar (widgets) on community pages. Does not affect "
"Jetonomy's own right-rail."
msgstr ""
"Nasconde la barra laterale (widget) del tuo tema nelle pagine della "
"community. Non influisce sulla barra laterale destra di Jetonomy."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:884
msgid "Page Padding"
msgstr "Spaziatura Pagina"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:894
msgid "None (edge to edge)"
msgstr "Nessuna (da bordo a bordo)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:899 includes/admin/views/settings.php:909
msgid "Comfortable"
msgstr "Comoda"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:905
msgid "Layout Density"
msgstr "Densità Layout"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:908
msgid "Compact"
msgstr "Compatta"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:910
msgid "Spacious"
msgstr "Spaziosa"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:920
msgid "Custom CSS"
msgstr "CSS Personalizzato"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:921
msgid ""
"Extra CSS injected into the community frontend. Use browser DevTools to "
"find selectors."
msgstr ""
"CSS extra iniettato nel frontend della community. Usa gli Strumenti per "
"sviluppatori del browser per trovare i selettori."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:935 includes/admin/views/settings.php:1305
msgid "White Label"
msgstr "Etichetta Bianca"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:936
msgid "Remove Jetonomy branding and replace it with your own logo and color scheme."
msgstr ""
"Rimuovi il branding Jetonomy e sostituiscilo con il tuo logo e schema di "
"colori."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:946
msgid "Title Templates"
msgstr "Modelli di Titolo"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:947
msgid "Control how page titles are formatted for community pages."
msgstr ""
"Controlla come i titoli delle pagine vengono formattati nelle pagine della "
"community."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:951
msgid "Post Title"
msgstr "Titolo Post"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:954
msgid "Tokens: {post_title}, {space_name}, {site_name}"
msgstr "Token: {post_title}, {space_name}, {site_name}"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:958
msgid "Space Title"
msgstr "Titolo Space"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:961
msgid "Tokens: {space_name}, {site_name}"
msgstr "Token: {space_name}, {site_name}"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:970
msgid "Structured Data & Indexing"
msgstr "Dati Strutturati e Indicizzazione"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:971
msgid "Schema markup, sitemap inclusion, and noindex rules."
msgstr "Markup schema, inclusione della mappa del sito e regole noindex."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:975
msgid "Schema Markup"
msgstr "Markup Schema"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:979
msgid "Enable DiscussionForumPosting schema on post pages"
msgstr "Abilita schema DiscussionForumPosting nelle pagine dei post"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:984
msgid "XML Sitemap"
msgstr "Sitemap XML"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:988
msgid "Include community pages in the WordPress XML sitemap"
msgstr "Includi le pagine della comunità nella sitemap XML di WordPress"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:993
msgid "Noindex"
msgstr "Noindex"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:998
msgid "Noindex user profile pages"
msgstr "Noindex delle pagine del profilo utente"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1003
msgid "Noindex search result pages"
msgstr "Noindex delle pagine dei risultati di ricerca"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1006
msgid ""
"Moderation queues, composer pages, notifications, edit profile, and invite "
"landings always emit noindex (administrative or personal views, not for "
"search results)."
msgstr ""
"Le code di moderazione, le pagine del compositore, le notifiche, la "
"modifica del profilo e le pagine di invito emettono sempre noindex "
"(visualizzazioni amministrative o personali, non per i risultati di "
"ricerca)."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1010
msgid "Twitter / X handle"
msgstr "Handle Twitter / X"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1013
msgid ""
"Site handle emitted as twitter:site on every public route. Leave blank to "
"omit."
msgstr ""
"Handle del sito emesso come twitter:site su ogni rotta pubblica. Lascia "
"vuoto per omettere."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1017
msgid "Default share image"
msgstr "Immagine di condivisione predefinita"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1020
msgid ""
"og:image URL when a route has no image of its own. Falls back to the "
"WordPress site logo / icon when this is empty."
msgstr ""
"URL og:image quando una rotta non ha un'immagine propria. Ritorna al logo / "
"icona del sito WordPress quando questo è vuoto."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1024
msgid "Verify SEO"
msgstr "Verifica SEO"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1027
msgid "Open XML sitemap"
msgstr "Apri sitemap XML"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1029
msgid ""
"Confirms /wp-sitemap.xml is reachable and that community URLs (spaces + "
"posts) are listed. New spaces can take a few minutes to appear after the "
"next ping."
msgstr ""
"Conferma che /wp-sitemap.xml è raggiungibile e che gli URL della comunità "
"(Spaces + posts) sono elencati. I nuovi Spaces potrebbero impiegare alcuni "
"minuti per comparire dopo il prossimo ping."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1038
msgid "Social Embeds (Instagram & Facebook)"
msgstr "Social Embeds (Instagram & Facebook)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1040
msgid ""
"YouTube, Vimeo, TikTok, Twitter/X, Spotify, SoundCloud, and TED Talks embed "
"automatically with no setup required. Instagram and Facebook require a free "
"Meta Developer App because Meta deprecated anonymous oEmbed access in "
"October 2020."
msgstr ""
"YouTube, Vimeo, TikTok, Twitter/X, Spotify, SoundCloud e TED Talks si "
"incorporano automaticamente senza configurazione richiesta. Instagram e "
"Facebook richiedono un'app Meta Developer gratuita perché Meta ha deprecato "
"l'accesso anonimo a oEmbed nell'ottobre 2020."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1045
msgid "Facebook App ID"
msgstr "ID dell'app Facebook"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1048
msgid "Numeric App ID from your Meta Developer dashboard."
msgstr "ID dell'app numerica dal tuo dashboard Meta Developer."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1052
msgid "Facebook App Secret"
msgstr "Secret dell'app Facebook"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1055
msgid "Secret is stored in wp_options and never exposed to the frontend."
msgstr "Il segreto è archiviato in wp_options e mai esposto al frontend."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1062
msgid "How to create a Facebook App (5 minutes, free)"
msgstr "Come creare un'app Facebook (5 minuti, gratuito)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1069
#. translators: 1: developers.facebook.com URL, 2: Create App button label
msgid ""
"Go to %1$s and log in with a Facebook account. Click %2$s in the top-right "
"corner."
msgstr ""
"Vai a %1$s e accedi con un account Facebook. Fai clic su %2$s nell'angolo "
"in alto a destra."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1071
msgid "Create App"
msgstr "Crea app"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1079
#. translators: 1: "Other" use-case label, 2: "Business" app type label
msgid ""
"When asked \"What do you want your app to do?\", pick %1$s. When asked for "
"the app type, pick %2$s. Name it anything, e.g. \"My Forum Embeds\"."
msgstr ""
"Quando ti viene chiesto \"Cosa vuoi che la tua app faccia?\", scegli %1$s. "
"Quando ti viene chiesto il tipo di app, scegli %2$s. Chiamala come "
"preferisci, ad es. \"I miei embed del forum\"."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1081
msgid "Business"
msgstr "Business"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1089
#. translators: %s: "oEmbed Read" product label
msgid ""
"On the new app's dashboard, find the %s product in the Products list and "
"click Set Up. It's free."
msgstr ""
"Nel dashboard della tua nuova app, trova il prodotto %s nell'elenco "
"Prodotti e fai clic su Configura. È gratuito."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1090
msgid "oEmbed Read"
msgstr "oEmbed Read"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1098
#. translators: 1: "Settings > Basic" breadcrumb, 2: App ID label, 3: App
#. Secret label
msgid "Open %1$s. Copy the %2$s and %3$s and paste them into the two fields above."
msgstr "Apri %1$s. Copia %2$s e %3$s e incollali nei due campi sopra."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1099
msgid "Settings → Basic"
msgstr "Impostazioni → Base"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1100
msgid "App ID"
msgstr "ID dell'app"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1101
msgid "App Secret"
msgstr "Secret dell'app"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1109
#. translators: 1: "App Review > Requests" breadcrumb, 2: "oembed_read"
#. permission name
msgid ""
"Go to %1$s and request the %2$s permission. Meta typically approves in 1–3 "
"business days. Your app stays in Development Mode until approved; embeds "
"will work for the admin who created the app even before approval."
msgstr ""
"Vai a %1$s e richiedi il permesso %2$s. Meta generalmente approva in 1–3 "
"giorni lavorativi. La tua app rimane in modalità sviluppo fino "
"all'approvazione; gli embed funzioneranno per l'admin che ha creato l'app "
"anche prima dell'approvazione."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1110
msgid "App Review → Requests"
msgstr "Revisione dell'app → Richieste"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1116
msgid ""
"Save the settings here. Instagram and Facebook URLs pasted into posts and "
"replies will now unfurl as rich embeds."
msgstr ""
"Salva le impostazioni qui. Gli URL di Instagram e Facebook incollati nei "
"post e nelle risposte ora si espanderanno come embed avanzati."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1120
msgid "Privacy note:"
msgstr "Nota sulla privacy:"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1121
msgid ""
"Jetonomy only sends oEmbed requests to Meta when a user pastes an "
"Instagram/Facebook URL. No tracking, no user data: just the public post URL "
"and your app token. Leave these fields blank to skip Instagram/Facebook "
"embeds entirely; the URL will render as a plain clickable link."
msgstr ""
"Jetonomy invia richieste oEmbed a Meta solo quando un utente incolla un URL "
"di Instagram/Facebook. Nessun tracciamento, nessun dato utente: solo l'URL "
"del post pubblico e il token della tua app. Lascia questi campi vuoti per "
"saltare completamente gli embed di Instagram/Facebook; l'URL verrà "
"visualizzato come un semplice collegamento cliccabile."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1129
#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1299
msgid "SEO Pro"
msgstr "SEO Pro"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1130
msgid ""
"Open Graph tags, per-space canonical URLs, breadcrumb schema, and advanced "
"robots control."
msgstr ""
"Tag Open Graph, URL canonici per Space, schema breadcrumb e controllo "
"avanzato dei robot."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1140
msgid "CAPTCHA Provider"
msgstr "Provider CAPTCHA"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1141
msgid ""
"Protect post and reply forms from bots. Trusted members (trust level 2+) "
"are always exempt."
msgstr ""
"Proteggi i moduli di post e risposta dai bot. I membri attendibili (Trust "
"Level 2+) sono sempre esenti."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1150
msgid ""
"A CAPTCHA provider is selected but the Site Key and/or Secret Key is empty. "
"The CAPTCHA will not render until both keys are filled in."
msgstr ""
"Un provider CAPTCHA è selezionato ma il Site Key e/o il Secret Key è vuoto. "
"Il CAPTCHA non verrà visualizzato finché entrambe le chiavi non saranno "
"compilate."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1152
msgid ""
"CAPTCHA keys are saved but the Provider is set to Disabled, so no CAPTCHA "
"renders. Select Cloudflare Turnstile or reCAPTCHA above to activate it."
msgstr ""
"Le chiavi CAPTCHA sono salvate ma il Provider è impostato su Disabilitato, "
"quindi nessun CAPTCHA viene visualizzato. Seleziona Cloudflare Turnstile o "
"reCAPTCHA sopra per attivarlo."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1157
msgid "Heads up:"
msgstr "Attenzione:"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1165
msgid "Provider"
msgstr "Provider"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1168
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Disabilitato"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1169
msgid "Google reCAPTCHA v3 (invisible)"
msgstr "Google reCAPTCHA v3 (invisibile)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1170
msgid "Cloudflare Turnstile (privacy-friendly)"
msgstr "Cloudflare Turnstile (rispettoso della privacy)"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1175
msgid "Site Key"
msgstr "Chiave del Sito"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1179
msgid "reCAPTCHA: get keys at"
msgstr "reCAPTCHA: ottieni le chiavi su"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1181
msgid "Turnstile: get keys at"
msgstr "Turnstile: ottieni le chiavi su"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1187
msgid "Secret Key"
msgstr "Chiave Segreta"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1190
msgid "Stored securely. Never shared with visitors."
msgstr "Archiviato in modo sicuro. Mai condiviso con i visitatori."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1194
msgid "Score Threshold"
msgstr "Soglia di Punteggio"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1197
msgid ""
"reCAPTCHA v3 only. Scores below this value are treated as bots (0.1 = "
"permissive, 0.9 = strict). Default: 0.5."
msgstr ""
"Solo reCAPTCHA v3. I punteggi al di sotto di questo valore vengono trattati "
"come bot (0.1 = permissivo, 0.9 = rigoroso). Predefinito: 0.5."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1208
msgid "Unlock 13 Pro Extensions"
msgstr "Sblocca 13 Estensioni Pro"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1210
msgid ""
"Your community is growing. Give it reactions, messaging, polls, analytics, "
"badges, webhooks, and more. Each feature is an independent module you "
"enable only when you need it."
msgstr ""
"La tua comunità sta crescendo. Dai reazioni, messaggistica, sondaggi, "
"analitiche, badge, webhook e altro. Ogni funzione è un modulo indipendente "
"che abiliti solo quando ne hai bisogno."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1213
msgid "Get Jetonomy Pro. Starting at $69/yr."
msgstr "Ottieni Jetonomy Pro. A partire da $69/anno."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1218
#. translators: %s: coupon code
msgid "Use code %s for 30%% off lifetime plans."
msgstr "Usa il codice %s per il 30%% di sconto sui piani a vita."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1227
msgid "Pro Extensions"
msgstr "Estensioni Pro"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1228
msgid ""
"Each extension is independent. Enable only what you need. Disabled "
"extensions load zero code."
msgstr ""
"Ogni estensione è indipendente. Abilita solo ciò di cui hai bisogno. Le "
"estensioni disabilitate caricano zero codice."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1233
msgid "Emoji Reactions"
msgstr "Reazioni Emoji"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1235
msgid "Like, love, and celebrate with Slack-style reactions on posts and replies."
msgstr "Mi piace, ama e celebra con reazioni in stile Slack su post e risposte."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1239
msgid "Private Messaging"
msgstr "Messaggistica Privata"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1241
msgid "One-on-one and group conversations between community members."
msgstr "Conversazioni uno-a-uno e di gruppo tra i membri della comunità."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1245
msgid "Polls"
msgstr "Sondaggi"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1247
msgid "Create polls within posts for community voting and decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Crea sondaggi all'interno dei post per il voto della comunità e il processo "
"decisionale."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1251
msgid "Analytics Dashboard"
msgstr "Pannello Analytics"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1253
msgid "Engagement graphs, user growth, top spaces, post trends, and CSV export."
msgstr ""
"Grafici di coinvolgimento, crescita degli utenti, spazi principali, "
"tendenze dei post e esportazione CSV."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1257
msgid "Email Digests"
msgstr "Digest Email"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1259
msgid "Daily and weekly email digests of community activity for subscribed users."
msgstr ""
"Digest email giornalieri e settimanali dell'attività della comunità per gli "
"utenti iscritti."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1263
msgid "Web Push"
msgstr "Web Push"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1265
msgid "Browser push notifications for replies, mentions, and forum events."
msgstr "Notifiche push del browser per risposte, menzioni ed eventi del forum."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1269
msgid "Webhooks"
msgstr "Webhook"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1271
msgid ""
"Fire HTTP POST requests to Zapier, Slack, n8n, or any endpoint on forum "
"events."
msgstr ""
"Invia richieste HTTP POST a Zapier, Slack, n8n o qualsiasi endpoint su "
"eventi del forum."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1275
msgid "Reply by Email"
msgstr "Rispondi per Email"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1277
msgid "Members reply to notifications by email. No login required."
msgstr "I membri rispondono alle notifiche via email. Nessun login richiesto."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1281
msgid "Custom Badges"
msgstr "Badge Personalizzati"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1283
msgid "Create and auto-award custom badges based on community activity criteria."
msgstr ""
"Crea e auto-assegna badge personalizzati in base ai criteri di attività "
"della comunità."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1287
#: includes/admin/views/space-edit.php:47
msgid "Custom Fields"
msgstr "Campi Personalizzati"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1289
msgid ""
"Add custom fields to posts and user profiles: text, select, checkbox, date, "
"and more."
msgstr ""
"Aggiungi campi personalizzati a post e profili utente: testo, seleziona, "
"casella di controllo, data e altro."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1293
msgid "Advanced Moderation"
msgstr "Moderazione Avanzata"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1295
msgid ""
"Auto-moderation rules engine: keyword filters, regex, link limits, and spam "
"scoring."
msgstr ""
"Motore di auto-moderazione: filtri per parole chiave, regex, limiti di link "
"e valutazione dello spam."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1301
msgid ""
"Per-space meta titles, Open Graph, Twitter Cards, Schema.org, sitemap "
"controls."
msgstr ""
"Titoli meta per Space, Open Graph, Twitter Cards, Schema.org, controlli "
"della sitemap."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1307
msgid ""
"Replace all Jetonomy branding: custom logo, name, footer, accent color, and "
"CSS."
msgstr ""
"Sostituisci tutto il branding di Jetonomy: logo personalizzato, nome, "
"footer, colore di accento e CSS."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1332
msgid "Jetonomy Pro License"
